  "pageTitle": "C&D 廢棄物破碎機及回收骨料篩選廠",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section split-section\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">交鑰匙C&D廢棄物回收廠</p>\n          <h1>C&D 廢棄物破碎機及回收骨料篩選廠</h1>\n          <p class=\"hero-copy\">WEI LAN Lion One系統結合破碎、滾筒篩分、振動篩分、磁性分離、氣流分離、打包、稱重及數位控制，涵蓋C&D 廢棄物、裝飾廢棄物、拆除廢棄物及大型廢棄物專案。</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n            <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/contact\">請求提案</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <picture>\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"綜合C&D 廢棄物破碎與篩選站\">\n        </picture>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"core-parameters\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">核心參數</p>\n          <h2 id=\"core-parameters-title\">Lion One整合破碎與篩選站</h2>\n          <p>重型移動站設計用於建築、裝飾、拆除及大型廢棄物處理。四個核心參數皆依其工作範圍列出。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\">\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">綜合破碎與篩選站</p>\n                </div>\n                <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div><dt>製造集團</dt><dd>WEI&nbsp;LAN</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>類型</dt><dd>行動&nbsp;電台</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>等級</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div>\n                </dl>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">T/H</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>進給尺寸</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">mm</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>佔地</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\"><span class=\"spec-suffix-unit\">m<sup>2</sup></span> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>驅動</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液壓</span></dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n              <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">WEI LAN</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>寧波，中國</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>整合行動台</span>\n              </footer>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">線路模組</p>\n          <h2>緊湊的空間與完整的資源回收流程</h2>\n          <p>配置用於回收骨料回收、輕質物料分離、金屬移除、自動化控制及作業報告。</p>\n        </div>\n        <ol class=\"industrial-ledger\" role=\"list\">\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-01</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>Lion One車站</h3>\n              <p>整合破碎與篩選站，具備200 mm給料尺寸，35 m<sup>2</sup> 車身尺寸，並全液壓驅動。</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>給料</dt><dd>200 mm</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>驅動</dt><dd>液壓</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-02</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>20-70 t/h選項</h3>\n              <p>容量選項適用於不同的市政、工業及C&D 廢棄物資源利用專案。</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>分布範圍</dt><dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>分級</dt><dd>3 等級</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-03</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>分離模組</h3>\n              <p>支援 碎紙機、C&D 廢棄物篩網、回收骨料振動篩、C&D 廢棄物磁性分離器、C&D 廢棄物正負壓 氣流分離系統，以及打包機。</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>模組</dt><dd>6 階段</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>設定</dt><dd>模組化</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-04</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>PLC與DCS控制</h3>\n              <p>手動、自動及遠端控制模式 支援 啟動-停止控制、警示、稱重流量及報告。</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>模式</dt><dd>手冊 ·汽車 ·遠端</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>控制</dt><dd>PLC + DCS</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-process-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">流程概述</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-process-title\">混合輸入到可重複使用輸出的C&amp;D廢棄物流</h2>\n          <p>C&D 廢棄物管線透過受控的進料、破碎、篩選及最終回收處理，將混合的C&amp;D物料轉化為可重複使用的產出。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-flow\" aria-label=\"C&D 廢棄物回收流程\">\n          <div class=\"industrial-flow-track\">\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">01</span>\n              <h3>給料</h3>\n              <p>將建築、裝飾、拆除或大塊廢棄物送入整合處理線。</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"給料影片佔位符\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-01</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">02</span>\n              <h3>破碎</h3>\n              <p>將混合廢棄物減少為較易管理的顆粒大小，以便下游篩選與分離。</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"壓碎影片佔位符\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-02</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">03</span>\n              <h3>篩分</h3>\n              <p>依尺寸分離材料至 支援 骨料回收及更乾淨的下游處理。</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"篩分影片佔位符\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-03</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"industrial-flow-wrap\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-down\"></span>\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-arrow\"></span>\n          </div>\n          <article class=\"industrial-flow-node industrial-flow-finale\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">04</span>\n            <p class=\"industrial-flow-finale-eyebrow\">產出</p>\n            <h3>回收產物</h3>\n            <p>生產回收骨料和可重複使用的分餾物，準備下游再利用。</p>\n            <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"回收輸出影像佔位符\">\n              <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\">\n                <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-04</span>\n                <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </div>\n            </figure>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-compare-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">產品比較</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-compare-title\">Lion One 與 MK-F50 比較</h2>\n          <p>WEI LAN整合的C&amp;D廢棄物管線如何與典型多機場址配置的對比，並以驅動總擁有成本的指標相比較。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"product-compare-layout\">\n          <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"Lion One爆炸視角\">\n            <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸視圖即將推出\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·LION ONE</span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸視角即將登場</span>\n            </div>\n            <figcaption>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">整合行動站 ·重型</span>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n\n          <div class=\"product-compare-panel\">\n            <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>WEI LAN Lion One\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>GREATWALL HAVEY INDUSTRY MK-F50\n              </span>\n            </header>\n\n            <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span>\n                  <h3>佔地</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">整合站的 m²</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:79%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">35 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">44.2 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">整合式移動站取代了單一滑架中的多機場佈局。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span>\n                  <h3>容量</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">T/H額定範圍</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">20-70 t/h</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:88.6%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">40-62 t/h</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">容量條以 上限 額定吞吐量在70 t/h上限上調整，標籤則顯示每個型號的完整運作範圍。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span>\n                  <h3>功耗</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">千瓦每100 t/h</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:80%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">132 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">165 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按額定吞吐量計算，每噸分揀功率約降低25%。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span>\n                  <h3>運輸與組裝</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">服役天數</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:12%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">2–3 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">18 – 25 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">行動站使用標準 拖車 運輸;現場工作僅限於定位與接駁。</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section industrial-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">常見問題</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-faq-title\">專案規模調整前的C&amp;D廢棄物回收廠問題</h2>\n          <p>利用這些答案準備早期 供應商 比較、內部可行性審查及C&D 廢棄物回收設備的徵求條件（RFQ）資訊。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-faq-panel\">\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-01</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">什麼因素會影響C&amp;D廢棄物回收廠的成本？</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">成本取決於目標容量、進料量、所需輸出、破碎機與篩選範圍、磁性分離、氣流分離、打包、控制系統、場址配置及 支援的調試。</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n                <span>目標容量</span>\n                <span>場地配置</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-02</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">C&D 廢棄物管線能處理哪些材料？</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">該管線用於C&D 廢棄物、裝飾廢棄物、拆除廢棄物、大塊廢棄物，以及需要破碎、篩分、金屬回收和輕重分離的混合輕質物料。</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n                <span>廢棄物組成</span>\n                <span>資料照片或影片</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-03</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">通常包含哪些設備模組？</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">典型的生產線可能包括給料、破碎、滾筒篩分、振動篩分、C&amp;D廢棄物磁性分離器、氣流分離系統、打包機、稱重、PLC控制及遠端監控。</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n                <span>所需輸出規格</span>\n                <span>需要回收模組</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-04</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">買家應該如何選擇合適的容量？</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">運能應與每小時投入、物料密度、預期運作時間、輸出規格、當地運輸流量及場地佔地面積相匹配。WEI LAN可以在建議20-70 t/h配置前先檢視專案資料。</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n                <span>進給尺寸</span>\n                <span>營運時間與運作時間</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section industrial-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-rfq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ準備</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-rfq-title\">準備 C&amp;D 線路報價的資料包</h2>\n          <p>利用此清單準備足夠的工程背景，用於容量選擇、模組配置、運輸規劃及安裝審查。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-rfq-checklist\">\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-01</span>\n            <h3>廢棄物組成</h3>\n            <p>估算混凝土、磚塊、木材、塑膠、金屬、土壤、裝飾廢棄物、大塊廢棄物及輕質雜質的比例。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-02</span>\n            <h3>進給尺寸</h3>\n            <p>確認最大進貨尺寸、平均整塊大小、預分揀狀況，以及是否需要預先破碎的超大物料。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-03</span>\n            <h3>目標容量</h3>\n            <p>分享每小時吞吐量、工作班次、預期運作時間、季節負載變動及最終總體規格。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-04</span>\n            <h3>場地配置</h3>\n            <p>提供 可用可保護的封面、卡車移動路徑、電力存取、水與塵埃控制限制，以及排放儲存區。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求工程審查</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">準備檔案包</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
